 No imageUrl. Each item supports optional subtitle and required body."},ImageTopContentSlide:{props:X,description:"Card with title on top, then either a single horizontal visual strip with optional subtitle/body or an optional items array (1 to 4 columns). A root visual may stand alone without body when the visual carries the message. Each visual slot may be chart, generated image, visualCard, or placeholder. Each item has optional chart, optional visualPrompt for image generation, optional imageUrl (server may fill), optional visualCard, optional subtitle, and required body. Prefer items when parallel visuals plus copy fit the outline; use up to 4 columns when there are enough distinct points."},ImageOnlySlide:{props:K,description:"Visual-first slide: title plus either one legacy large visual slot (optional chart, visualPrompt, optional imageUrl) or an optional items grid (1 to 4) with optional title, chart, visualPrompt, and imageUrl per slot. Prefer items when multiple outline points deserve equal visual weight; use up to 4 items when the outline supports distinct visuals, charts, or concepts. Use chart for compact data visuals and visualPrompt for generated imagery; imageUrl is usually server-filled."},ImageTopTextSlide:{props:J,description:"Padded slide: wide visual slot on top (chart, generated image, or placeholder), then title, optional subtitle, and body. Use when a hero visual should lead with narrative below."},ImageBottomTextSlide:{props:J,description:"Padded slide: title, optional subtitle, and body first; wide visual slot at the bottom (chart, generated image, or placeholder). Use when copy should lead and the visual anchors underneath."},ImageTopBandTextSlide:{props:J,description:"Top visual band flush to slide top and sides; text block below with standard padding. Same props as ImageTopTextSlide, including optional chart for quantitative visuals."},ImageBottomBandTextSlide:{props:J,description:"Text block on top with padding; bottom visual band flush to slide bottom and sides. Same props as ImageTopTextSlide, including optional chart for quantitative visuals."},TextImageSquareSlide:{props:Z,description:"Card with narrative on the left and a fixed-width visual slot on the right. The visual slot may be chart, generated image, or placeholder."},ImageSquareTextSlide:{props:Z,description:"Mirror of TextImageSquareSlide: fixed-width visual slot on the left and narrative on the right. The visual slot may be chart, generated image, or placeholder."},TextCoverSlide:{props:$,description:"Text-only cover with title, optional subtitle, and body left-aligned in a single padded column. No visual slot — use when the opening should land on narrative alone."},TextCenteredCoverSlide:{props:$,description:"Text-only cover with title, optional subtitle, and body centered in the slide. No visual slot — use for hero/manifesto-style openings that should feel symmetric and declarative."},TextComponentSplitSlide:{props:ee,description:"Card with narrative on the left and a full-height visual panel on the right. The visual panel may be chart, generated image, or placeholder."}},actions:{}});e.s(["catalogNodeSchema",0,eh,"presentationV2Catalog",0,eA],314958);var eg=e.i(975157);function em({fieldPath:e,className:n,as:a="p",children:o,autoFocus:i=!1,placeholder:s,maxLength:l}){let{ref:c,isEditing:u,fontFamily:d,refreshActiveField:f,handleInput:p,handleBlur:h,handleKeyDown:A,handlePaste:g}=function({fieldPath:e,children:t,autoFocus:n,maxLength:a}){let{isEditing:o,onFieldChange:i,setActiveField:s,fontOverrides:l}=m(),c=(0,r.useRef)(null),u=l[e],d=(0,r.useRef)(t??""),f=(0,r.useRef)(!1);(0,r.useEffect)(()=>{let e=c.current;e&&(u?e.style.fontFamily=u:e.style.removeProperty("font-family"))},[u]),(0,r.useEffect)(()=>{let e=c.current;if(!e||document.activeElement===e)return;let r=t??"";d.current=r,f.current=!1,e.innerHTML!==r&&(e.innerHTML=r)},[t,o]),(0,r.useEffect)(()=>{n&&o&&c.current&&c.current.focus()},[n,o]);let p=(0,r.useCallback)(()=>{let t=c